rollingUpdate in K8
===============
what is rolling update ?
it is one of the application deployment strategies.! in Kubernetes
Old pods are gradually terminated while new pods are created, ensuring continuous availability of the application.

when do we do rolling update?
---------------------------------
purpose of doing rollingUpdate is to deploy #new applications #witout_downtime we use rollingUpdate
We use a Deployment resource in Kubernetes to achieve Rolling Updates.

#scenario:
------------
v1.12 ---> v1.13?
We have an application currently running on version v1.12, and we want to release a new version with additional features. To ensure zero downtime and continuous availability for users, we use the Rolling Update strategy, which gradually replaces old pods with new ones.

